 \int_0^1 \lfloor x+a\rfloor dx = \int_a^{\lceil a\rceil}\lfloor a\rfloor dx+\int_{\lceil a\rceil}^{a+1} \lceil a\rceil dx \\ = \lfloor a\rfloor(\lceil a\rceil-a)+\lceil a\rceil(a+1-\lceil a\rceil)\\ = (\lceil a\rceil -\lfloor a\rfloor)a + \lceil a\rceil(\lfloor a\rfloor+1-\lceil a\rceil)\\ =a 
